    "name": "SECTOR ZERO",
    "steam_appid": 2352050,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"> <br><strong>- 在小行星的内部深处 -</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2352050/extras/601a5d00ba0ae079b63870ef75319213.webp?t=1770933155\" width=615 height=60 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2352050/extras/e425024b6854df3e04d06ee70761d689.poster.avif?t=1770933155\" width=614 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2352050/extras/e425024b6854df3e04d06ee70761d689.webm?t=1770933155\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2352050/extras/e425024b6854df3e04d06ee70761d689.mp4?t=1770933155\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >SECTOR ZERO 是一个黑暗科幻主题，基于物理的短篇解谜冒险游戏。你扮演的是在小行星2031 XT深处被采矿作业唤醒的，古老的蜂巢思维实体的碎片。人类殖民者为求资源而将一块巨大的小行星逐渐分解，故事在这片宇宙深空中悄然展开。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>- 在太空中漂荡 -</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2352050/extras/9cb6a0fcb61943e760a0fc5a15d869de.webp?t=1770933155\" width=615 height=60 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2352050/extras/c59abb744893c5dffebdd5bf73f8ed33.poster.avif?t=1770933155\" width=614 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2352050/extras/c59abb744893c5dffebdd5bf73f8ed33.webm?t=1770933155\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2352050/extras/c59abb744893c5dffebdd5bf73f8ed33.mp4?t=1770933155\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >贪婪的矿工们挖得太深，在小行星的核心处挖到了他们绝不想碰到的东西——一个被称为<i>腐化</i>的古老蜂巢思维体。它从永恒的沉睡中醒来，在这座空间站的系统中蔓延，黑暗的触须扭曲了金属，机械，甚至人的思想。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>- 他们挖得太深了 -</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2352050/extras/02c956abd31ceee42960af5c6f56af62.webp?t=1770933155\" width=615 height=60 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2352050/extras/bb4d0ba2104b62de80c66d11a0836d72.poster.avif?t=1770933155\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2352050/extras/bb4d0ba2104b62de80c66d11a0836d72.webm?t=1770933155\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2352050/extras/bb4d0ba2104b62de80c66d11a0836d72.mp4?t=1770933155\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无数的激光、炮塔和自动防御系统试图阻止你。你唯一的优势是拥有腐化并控制人类科技的能力，让他们的创造物反过来对付他们。利用这种力量克服平台挑战并解决复杂的物理谜题。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>- 苏醒之物 -</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2352050/extras/9c22f1d0015c583883073d26363b7511.webp?t=1770933155\" width=615 height=60 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2352050/extras/1ec1ee72cc47b6477951142825e3bebf.poster.avif?t=1770933155\" width=614 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2352050/extras/1ec1ee72cc47b6477951142825e3bebf.webm?t=1770933155\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2352050/extras/1ec1ee72cc47b6477951142825e3bebf.mp4?t=1770933155\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >尽管腐化蔓延，被隔离的区域仍受人类控制——被封锁，被加固，誓死抵抗。你会适应并渗透他们，既然他们闯入了你的领地，那就送给他们应得的结局。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏特色：</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >约1小时主线剧情，和额外2小时的解密与成就探索。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >扮演怪物。在精心设计的环境中跳跃、攀登、阴暗地爬行。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与激光和炮塔斗智斗勇，或在潜行中绕过敌人。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >腐化人类的造物为己所用。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过完全基于物理的互动操控周围的环境。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >支持控制手柄与Steam Deck 。</p></li></ul>",
    "supported_languages": "英语<strong>*</strong>, 挪威语, 法语, 意大利语, 德语, 西班牙语 - 西班牙, 保加利亚语, 捷克语, 丹麦语, 荷兰语, 希腊语, 匈牙利语, 印度尼西亚语, 日语, 韩语, 波兰语, 葡萄牙语 - 巴西, 葡萄牙语 - 葡萄牙, 罗马尼亚语, 俄语, 简体中文, 西班牙语 - 拉丁美洲, 瑞典语, 泰语, 繁体中文, 土耳其语, 乌克兰语, 越南语, 斯洛伐克语<br><strong>*</strong>具有完全音频支持的语言",
